{# #### `project_attributes_rag_knowledge_base_append_text` #}

{{SetCustomerMetadataAttribute(
    idn="project_attributes_rag_knowledge_base_append_text",
    field="multiple_fields",
    value={ "title": "3-06-A. RAG - Knowledge Base - Text [A]", "description": """Append additional text-based information to your RAG (Retrieval Augmented Generation) Knowledge
Base.

**Purpose:** This attribute allows you to incrementally add new knowledge without overwriting
existing entries. The system automatically processes this text, converts it into structured AKB
topics, and appends them to your agent's knowledge base.

**Usage:**

- Paste the text you want the agent to learn into this field.
- Once the agent has finished processing the information, this field will be cleared automatically.
- A historical record of this addition will be logged in the
  `project_attributes_rag_knowledge_base_append_text_log` field immediately after successful
  processing.

**Important Constraints:**

- **Character Limit:** Current input limit is ~100,000 characters. Exceeding this may cause
  processing errors.
- **Processing Time:** Transformation is asynchronous. Processing typically takes a few minutes but
  may take longer depending on the volume of data provided.

**Workflow:**

1. You provide the text here.
2. The content is converted into a format the agent understands
   (`project_attributes_private_dynamic_rag_knowledge_base_append_text_structured`).
3. New AKB topics are created under the `GeneralManagerAgent` and tagged with
   `rag_autogenerated_from_text`.
4. A copy of the text is saved to your history log (`..._log`), and this field is reset to empty.

**Key Behaviors:**

- **Independence:** Your \"Text memory\" and \"Website memory\" are separate. Resetting one does not
  affect the other.
- **Equality:** The agent treats information from text and websites with the same importance,
  choosing what to use based on how relevant it is to the current conversation.
- **Freshness:** Newer records are prioritized over older ones if they contain similar or updated
  information.
- **Updates:** To update information you've previously added, use the
  `project_attributes_rag_knowledge_base_append_text_reset` attribute to clear the memory before
  adding the new version.""", "group": "3. Knowledge Base", "value_type": "string", "is_hidden": False }
)}}

{# #### `project_attributes_rag_knowledge_base_append_text_log` #}

{{SetCustomerMetadataAttribute(
    idn="project_attributes_rag_knowledge_base_append_text_log",
    field="multiple_fields",
    value={ "title": "3-06-B. RAG - Knowledge Base - Text - Log [A]", "description": """A history of all the text you have added to the agent's memory.

