    value={ "title": "3-06-C. RAG - Knowledge Base - Text - Reset [A]", "description": """A switch to clear all the text-based information the agent has learned.

**Purpose:** Set this attribute to `True` to completely wipe all AKB topics generated from text
sources (specifically those labeled `rag_autogenerated_from_text`).

**Behavior:**

1. **Immediate Action:** When set to `True`, the system deletes all relevant AKB topics.
