- The newest entries appear at the bottom.

**Recovery:** If you need the agent to re-read a site after a reset, you can copy the URLs and
instructions from here back into the `append_websites` field.

**Constraints:**

- **Capacity:** This log has a maximum capacity of ~180,000 characters.
- **Auto-Cleanup:** When the limit is reached, the oldest entries are automatically removed to make
  room for new ones.""", "group": "3. Knowledge Base", "value_type": "string", "is_hidden": False }
)}}

